---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Cookie Policy
description: Cookie policy for MyWebClass.org
---

<div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
  <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: December 5, 2024</em></p>

  <section class="mb-3xl">
    <h2>What Are Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and provide information to website owners.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-3xl">
    <h2>How We Use Cookies</h2>
    <p>MyWebClass.org uses cookies for the following purposes:</p>

    <h3>Essential Cookies (Always Active)</h3>
    <p>These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be disabled:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Consent Management:</strong> Remembers your cookie preferences</li>
      <li><strong>Session Management:</strong> Maintains your browsing session</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Analytics Cookies (Optional)</h3>
    <p>These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Page Views:</strong> Tracks which pages are visited</li>
      <li><strong>Demo Interactions:</strong> Records clicks on design demos</li>
      <li><strong>Navigation Patterns:</strong> Helps us improve site organization</li>
      <li><strong>User Identification:</strong> Anonymous user ID for analytics</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Note:</strong> Analytics cookies are only set after you provide explicit consent.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-3xl">
    <h2>Cookie Details</h2>

    <h3>Essential Cookies</h3>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">
      <thead>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-black);">
          <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Name</th>
          <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Purpose</th>
          <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Duration</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);">
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">cookie-consent</td>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Stores your cookie preferences</td>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">1 year</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">session-id</td>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Anonymous session identifier</td>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Session</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 class="mt-xl">Analytics Cookies (If Consented)</h3>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">
      <thead>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-black);">
          <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Name</th>
          <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Purpose</th>
          <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Duration</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);">
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">analytics-consent</td>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Records analytics permission</td>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">1 year</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">user-id</td>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Anonymous user identifier</td>
          <td style="padding: var(--spacing-sm);">Persistent</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-3xl">
    <h2>Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h2>
    <p>You can manage your cookie preferences in several ways:</p>

    <h3>Through Our Website</h3>
    <p>
      Use our cookie preferences center to enable or disable analytics cookies at any time.
    </p>
    <button id="open-cookie-prefs" class="button button-primary mt-md">Manage Cookie Preferences</button>

    <h3>Through Your Browser</h3>
    <p>
      Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings. However, if you disable essential cookies, some features of the website may not function properly.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-3xl">
    <h2>Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We do not use third-party advertising or tracking cookies. All analytics are collected directly by us and stored in our own database.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-3xl">
    <h2>Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-3xl">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at:
      <br><strong>hello@mywebclass.org</strong>
    </p>
  </section>
</div>

{% block scripts %}
<script>
  document.getElementById('open-cookie-prefs')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const modal = document.getElementById('cookie-preferences-modal');
    if (modal) {
      modal.classList.add('visible');
      modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'false');
    }
  });
</script>
{% endblock %}
